				content: "It would appear from this verse that the authors of confusion in the Galatian church represented St Paul himself as recommending circumcision to his Gentile converts. It is difficult to understand how they can have found any colour for such statements, if this letter was written after the deliberations mentioned in Ac. 15; cf. Ac. 16.4."
